{"tid":297523,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"14年世界盃，俄羅斯涉嫌全隊服用禁藥","createTime":"2017-06-25T14:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T16:06:14.000Z","uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd9ba85dc387c2668d89e958c0713e8c1786bb3","tid":297523,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:10:23.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=LTzzvkjtUyhjop8rH7LtOqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f2ec1f5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】俄羅斯剛於周六以1:2不敵墨西哥，在洲際盃出局，同時被指球隊在2014世界盃涉嫌全隊服用禁藥，可說雙重打擊。<br />\n國際足協已經證實，目前正在調查俄羅斯國家隊在2014年世界盃有否禁藥，當時全部23名俄羅斯國腳都涉嫌服用禁藥。俄羅斯在該屆世界盃未曾贏過1場比賽，只能賽和韓國和阿爾及利亞，以及不敵比利時，當時教練卡比路被炒。據報球員的名字都在俄羅斯體壇集體使用禁藥的名單上，早前俄羅斯體壇被爆集體使用禁藥，逾1000名俄羅斯運動員在政府的策劃下服用禁藥，涉及30多個體育項目，影響了包括田徑、游泳及舉重等運動員。有關部門希望確定俄羅斯足球員有否參與禁藥風波，相信今次事件會對明年舉辦世界盃的俄羅斯造成重大打擊。"},{"pid":"3362122ed26909b12328f77475a1f98d46a0d965","tid":297523,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:12:41.000Z","msg":"食左禁藥都咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b3ca62d419564e0920a004593a5de518f67798","tid":297523,"uid":15370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:23:06.000Z","msg":"14仲有冇小學雞"},{"pid":"1a67833a0f6f18c307807933e24b3d45d596b316","tid":297523,"uid":9263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:17:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>14仲有冇小學雞</blockquote><br />\n無選佢."},{"pid":"ffa309528d11f80c2ae4675a68669d1dbd445be7","tid":297523,"uid":4706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:55:11.000Z","msg":"見到topic淨係諗起除疤膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9539eef6a22909e7a1b96819b054900172c7ee0